<h2>Add a team member to a work item</h2>

<p>To add a team member to a work item:</p>

<ol>
    <li>Go to the work item details page by clicking on a work item from the <strong>Work reporting</strong> page</li>
    <li>Click on the <strong>Team</strong> tab</li>
    <li>Click the <strong>Add team member</strong> button</li>
    <li>Search for the person using the staff search (they must be in Entra ID/Azure AD)</li>
    <li>Fill in the team member details:
        <ul>
            <li>Role (required)</li>
            <li>Funding arrangement (Admin or Programme)</li>
            <li>Time allocation (optional)</li>
            <li>Employment type (Permanent or MSP)</li>
            <li>Team status (current or previous)</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Click <strong>Add team member</strong> to save</li>
</ol>

<h3>Tips</h3>
<ul>
    <li>You can only add people who are in Entra ID/Azure AD</li>
    <li>If someone has left the team, you can mark them as "previous" rather than removing them</li>
    <li>You can edit or remove team members from the Team tab</li>
</ul>

